{"tid":2402252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"私了狗帶碼，事在必行","createTime":"2021-02-10T10:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T00:56:16.000Z","uid":304769,"like":627,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"08f02615f226f8e895e3a435bc82f32be9b68d40","tid":2402252,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:19:54.000Z","msg":"狗帶碼，一係有個QR code你掃佢，一係有個reader你比手機佢嘟，後者暫時未有（支那有，香港遲早有）<br />\n<br />\n只有有人<span class=\"red\"><strong>唔小心整污糟QR code一部分</strong></span>，例如倒瀉油漆或者痴張強力貼紙上去，成個QR code就廢左，reader亦都係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其次，如果有人無鳩聊，多手走去<span class=\"red\"><strong>將其他地方狗帶碼，print出黎，痴去另外一個狗帶碼</strong></span>，咁掃左個假碼既人，行程紀錄就會錯鳩曬。重點係有排都未有人發現有問題。<br />\n<br />\n以上方法再昇華，<strong><span class=\"red\">QR code其實可以自己加信息</span></strong>，如果有人將：&ldquo;你已經接觸新冠病毒患者，請即前往就近警署備案&rdquo;。咁嘟到假QR code條廢老就會比你嚇餐飽。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">以上都係違法行為，大家千祈唔好咁做</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n各位黑警同志，記得24小時寸步不離守著d狗帶碼啊<br />\n<br />\n教大家三招收狗帶碼皮<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2295674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2295674</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3c494c0719c52423bcc11e2f0899a8c12a006e2c","tid":2402252,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:20:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a09529ac56197223ce55ee81e96760046c1f87f","tid":2402252,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:25:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6590e78613887518da51aae2c52bd9b953cbdfec","tid":2402252,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0347fce8555c18b468dd52b478821c3ab6eabf0","tid":2402252,"uid":167340,"like":71,"dislike":2,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\nBtw,  scan 掃瞄 嘟 <br />\n掃乜9"},{"pid":"5e37e58e72ff970948fa2c7fb46dd438dca9f33f","tid":2402252,"uid":220942,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-1