95e3a435bc82f32be9b68d40","tid":2402252,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:19:54.000Z","msg":"狗帶碼，一係有個QR code你掃佢，一係有個reader你比手機佢嘟，後者暫時未有（支那有，香港遲早有）<br />\n<br />\n只有有人<span class=\"red\"><strong>唔小心整污糟QR code一部分</strong></span>，例如倒瀉油漆或者痴張強力貼紙上去，成個QR code就廢左，reader亦都係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其次，如果有人無鳩聊，多手走去<span class=\"red\"><strong>將其他地方狗帶碼，print出黎，痴去另外一個狗帶碼</strong></span>，咁掃左個假碼既人，行程紀錄就會錯鳩曬。重點係有排都未有人發現有問題。<br />\n<br />\n以上方法再昇華，<strong><span class=\"red\">QR code其實可以自己加信息</span></strong>，如果有人將：&ldquo;你已經接觸新冠病毒患者，請即前往就近警署備案&rdquo;。咁嘟到假QR code條廢老就會比你嚇餐飽。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">以上都係違法行為，大家千祈唔好咁做</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n各位黑警同志，記得24小時寸步不離守著d狗帶碼啊<br />\n<br />\n教大家三招收狗帶碼皮<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2295674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2295674</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"四個角粒黑點樣衰咗已經唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622938cc683cd009ce6b7e798baa1d9c2bac3a6a","tid":2402252,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d3ce8fe9a4facd5a6276edfb66dd8e02441cdb7d","tid":2402252,"uid":122514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf201d8e95a245e04b80270027bce5168b26bdff","tid":2402252,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ffa4fab38bd5dff2967aedf159b5793e32359ed","tid":2402252,"uid":122514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:55:02.000Z","msg":"集合藍店code 封區個晚不停scan"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:56:26.000Z","msg":"咩意思？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:58:16.000Z","msg":"touchwood中咗track返行蹤係咪會封店清潔<br />\n定強制班人做檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"咪傻，第一日認識港共咩？<br />\n<br />\n支那狗、藍店、藍絲、黑警向來都係有特權"},{"pid":"6318016753f2be4479695076e9af06d47a11d3a3","tid":2402252,"uid":304769,"